    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Jointed plates or leaves that allow swinging motion in a single plane of one of the members to which they are attached, such as a door or gate, and formed in the shape of the letter 'H' but with an additional right-angled element on one component of the hinge.</Note_Text>
